# safe-shell.tape — vhs script for the safe-shell demo GIF.

Output "demos/safe-shell.gif"

Set Theme "GitHub Dark"
Set FontFamily "JetBrains Mono"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1080
Set Height 720
Set Padding 24
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0
Set Framerate 24

Hide
Type "clear && bash demos/scenario-safe-shell.sh"
Enter
Show

Sleep 14s
